amples/46-workflow-crystallizer.prose:37:    Determine the right abstraction level for workflows.\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/46-workflow-crystallizer.prose:96:      Does the observed workflow overlap with existing examples?\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/48-habit-miner.prose:2:# Excavates your AI session history to find recurring workflows worth automating\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/48-habit-miner.prose:130:    You write .prose programs from mature workflow patterns.\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/48-habit-miner.prose:135:    - Design appropriate agents for the workflow\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/48-habit-miner.prose:400:  - A directory path (e.g., ~/my-workflows/)\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/README.md:3:These examples demonstrate workflows using OpenProse's full feature set.\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/README.md:15:| `05-debug-issue.prose`            | Step-by-step debugging workflow              |\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/README.md:17:| `07-refactor.prose`               | Systematic refactoring workflow              |\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/README.md:114:| `45-plugin-release.prose`            | OpenProse plugin release workflow (this repo)                      |\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/examples/README.md:115:| `46-workflow-crystallizer.prose`     | Reflective: observes thread, extracts workflow, writes .prose      |\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/guidance/antipatterns.md:151:#### copy-paste-workflows\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/guidance/antipatterns.md:156:# Bad: Duplicated workflow\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/guidance/antipatterns.md:170:**Why it's bad**: If the workflow needs to change, you must change it everywhere. Easy to miss one.\nextensions/open-prose/skills/prose/guidance/antipatterns.md:543:**Why it's bad**: Main workflow blocked by non-critical operation.\nextension