{"type":"message","id":"119f5fa4","parentId":"413bf473","timestamp":"2026-03-12T07:10:54.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"LINE プラグインの設定復旧、任せて！🔧\n\nまず設定を復元する前に、今の状況を把握するね：\n\n1. **設定ファイルの確認** - `~/.openclaw/config` や `.env` などにある LINE 関連の設定を確認\n2. **トークンの状態** - LINE ボットトークン、Channel Access Token の有効期限や破損がないか確認\n3. **extensions/line ディレクトリ** - プラグインコード自体が無傷か確認\n\n手早くやってみよう！まずは設定ファイルと extensions を探して。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_a0d52d79-00eb-45ae-a0c2-686fd38f8b5a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw -name \"*.env\" -o -name \"*config*\" -o -name \"credentials.json\" 2>/dev/null | head -30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\downl\\.openclaw\\workspace-desktop-stack","env":"[]"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen3.5:9b","usage":{"input":30146,"output":393,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30539,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773299454717}}
