{"type":"message","id":"7abc08bf","parentId":"6d2ee4d8","timestamp":"2026-03-12T07:13:18.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PowerShell の `find` コマンド（其实是 `Get-ChildItem`）が返却できない。Windows なので、単純なファイル検索を PowerShell で直接やろう：\n\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path ~/.openclaw -Recurse -Include \"*.env\",\"*config*\", \"credentials.json\" | Select-Object FullName -First 30\n```\n\nしかし `~` は Windows では `C:\\Users\\downl` になる。環境変数を展開して検索しよう：\n\n<tool_call>\n<function=exec>\n<parameter=command>\n$env:HOME; Get-ChildItem -Path $env:HOME -Recurse -Include \"*.env\",\"*config*\", \"credentials.json\" 2>$null | Select-Object FullName -First 30\n</parameter>\n<parameter=workdir>\nC:\\Users\\downl\\.openclaw\\workspace-desktop-stack\n</parameter>\n</function>\n</tool_call>"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen3.5:9b","usage":{"input":30762,"output":204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773299598563}}
